28
00:03:18,360 --> 00:03:20,890
Naturally, she wasn't as loved as her sister.

29
00:03:22,040 --> 00:03:23,170
Please, have a seat.

30
00:03:31,960 --> 00:03:32,840
After Wanrou

31
