54
00:04:46,040 --> 00:04:47,800
These dancers

55
00:04:48,000 --> 00:04:49,560
love her very much.

56
00:04:53,760 --> 00:04:57,040
Where did Wanrou jump into the river?

57
00:04:59,000 --> 00:05:01,440
Tianhe, west of the city.

58
00:05:02,800 --> 00:05:03,400
Slow down.

59
00:05:06,320 --> 00:05:07,720
According to Constable Su's orders,

60
00:05:07,720 --> 00:05:09,580
I was arranging for a night watch.

61
00:05:09,760 --> 00:05:11,640
I saw Wanqing leave this room

62
00:05:11,720 --> 00:05:13,120
