86
00:06:12,000 --> 00:06:12,800
As for us,

87
00:06:13,960 --> 00:06:15,280
next,

88
00:06:15,880 --> 00:06:17,340
Dad, did you figure it out?

89
00:06:17,640 --> 00:06:19,170
Let's go eat roast chicken.

90
00:06:19,480 --> 00:06:21,720
