94
00:06:26,200 --> 00:06:27,800
We are investigating a case.

95
00:06:27,800 --> 00:06:28,840
I don't want to eat it.

96
00:06:28,840 --> 00:06:30,300
It's your mother who does.

97
00:06:30,320 --> 00:06:32,720
She keeps asking for it ever since she tried it.

98
00:06:32,720 --> 00:06:33,760
I have to bring some back for her.

99
00:06:33,760 --> 00:06:34,680
Besides,

100
00:06:34,880 --> 00:06:37,159
investigating cases in the future

101
00:06:37,200 --> 00:06:39,440
