102
00:06:41,120 --> 00:06:41,680
As for me,

103
00:06:41,720 --> 00:06:43,880
I'm just a greedy old man about to retire.

104
00:06:43,880 --> 00:06:46,080
The best advice I can give you is

105
00:06:46,280 --> 00:06:49,480
