Remember what I always tell you.

107
00:06:53,840 --> 00:06:55,320
Safety first.

108
00:06:55,360 --> 00:06:57,159
Cases can wait.

109
00:06:57,200 --> 00:06:58,880
Got it, Dad. We know.

110
00:07:07,720 --> 00:07:09,320
Constable Su, you're early.

111
00:07:10,240 --> 00:07:11,700
Thanks for your hard work.

112
00:07:19,280 --> 00:07:20,880
Dongling, stop right there.

113
00:07:26,400 --> 00:07:29,240
This performance was booked by the Guan family long ago,

114
00:07:29,240 --> 00:07:31,680
