137
00:08:25,120 --> 00:08:26,240
Stop arguing.

138
00:08:29,560 --> 00:08:30,640
Tomorrow,

139
00:08:31,600 --> 00:08:32,840
I will dance.

140
00:09:20,680 --> 00:09:21,720
Miss Mingzhu.

141
00:09:28,840 --> 00:09:30,560
Sister Chunyi has to watch the shop today.

142
00:09:30,560 --> 00:09:31,560
She specially told me,

143
00:09:31,560 --> 00:09:33,160
since today is your brother's funeral,

144
00:09:33,160 --> 00:09:35,400
to bring some money to help out.

145
00:09:39,640 --> 00:09:41,300
Please take care of yourself.

146
00:09:52,480 --> 00:09:54,880
My brother ran a coffin shop for a long time.

147
00:09:55,080 --> 00:09:57,560
He made coffins for many people.

148
00:09:58,840 --> 00:10:01,760
In the past, I thought these coffins

149
00:10:02,360 --> 00:10:04,520
were prepared for others.

150
00:10:05,600 --> 00:10:07,080
Unexpectedly today,

151
00:10:07,600 --> 00:10:09,800
